1
00:00:14,580 --> 00:00:18,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have awaited your 
arrival, Wise Prince.</font>

2
00:00:19,410 --> 00:00:23,290
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="15"><font color="#efeee8">Ministry of Justice</font></font></font></b></font>

3
00:00:27,510 --> 00:00:29,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is truly an honor to meet you.</font>

4
00:00:29,930 --> 00:00:33,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am Viny Aussie,
Vice Minister of Justice.</font>

5
00:00:30,250 --> 00:00:33,880
<font face="Times New Roman" size="18" color="#d7dad8"><b>{\an3}<font color="#efefeb">Viny Aussie
<font size="13">Vice Minister of Justice</font></font></b></font>

6
00:00:33,970 --> 00:00:35,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My number two, eh?</i></font>

7
00:00:35,730 --> 00:00:38,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's young. Still on the rise, I'm sure.</i></font>

8
00:00:39,270 --> 00:00:41,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are my duties?</font>

9
00:00:41,980 --> 00:00:45,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Explain it to me.
A rough outline will do.</font>

10
00:00:45,390 --> 00:00:48,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course. You have two primary duties.</font>

11
00:00:48,310 --> 00:00:53,280
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="15"><font face="Arial"><font color="#dcdcdc">Meeres Empire</font></font></font></font>

12
00:00:48,320 --> 00:00:52,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First is the coordination of all 
courthouses across the empire.</font>

13
00:00:53,270 --> 00:00:59,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our ministry also tries many 
cases that occur in the capital.</font>

14
00:00:59,480 --> 00:01:02,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And, as with the rebellion six years ago,</font>

15
00:01:04,050 --> 00:01:08,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it is customary for the ministry 
or the emperor himself</font>

16
00:01:08,690 --> 00:01:13,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to judge those who commit serious 
crimes such as insurrection.</font>

17
00:01:13,080 --> 00:01:17,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So in other words, the ministry also 
functions as a common courthouse.</font>

18
00:01:18,330 --> 00:01:19,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That is correct.</font>

19
00:01:20,210 --> 00:01:21,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you try cases, as well?</font>

20
00:01:23,060 --> 00:01:24,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Depending on the case.</font>

21
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:27,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And how much do you receive in bribes?</font>

22
00:01:28,950 --> 00:01:31,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I do no such thing!</font>

23
00:01:31,690 --> 00:01:34,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not trying to force 
you into admitting guilt.</font>

24
00:01:34,730 --> 00:01:36,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I only want to know the real story.</font>

25
00:01:36,980 --> 00:01:39,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll forget as soon as I leave this room.</font>

26
00:01:39,500 --> 00:01:41,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just tell me the truth.</font>

27
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:46,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I might have expected as much.</font>

28
00:01:46,890 --> 00:01:48,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I, personally, do not accept many bribes.</font>

29
00:01:49,460 --> 00:01:52,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A few hundred rean annually,
I suppose.</font>

30
00:01:55,060 --> 00:01:56,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a rule, you see.</font>

31
00:01:57,330 --> 00:02:00,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those beneath me accept at 
least ten times that much.</font>

32
00:02:00,540 --> 00:02:01,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What rule?</font>

33
00:02:02,370 --> 00:02:04,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do not accept bribes 
in cases of murder.</font>

34
00:02:04,880 --> 00:02:05,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why is that?</font>

35
00:02:06,230 --> 00:02:07,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is too easily exposed.</font>

36
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:11,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If the accuser bears a grudge, 
I could become a target for revenge,</font>

37
00:02:11,070 --> 00:02:13,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">leading to irreparable damage.</font>

38
00:02:13,730 --> 00:02:18,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I accept bribes only in cases that 
could easily go in either direction.</font>

39
00:02:24,620 --> 00:02:25,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness?</font>

40
00:02:28,540 --> 00:02:32,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Assuming you take 500 in a year, I'll 
give you 5,000, ten times that.</font>

41
00:02:32,920 --> 00:02:35,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You will not accept bribes while I'm here.</font>

42
00:02:37,710 --> 00:02:41,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to live up to the emperor's 
expectations. Please help me do so.</font>

43
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:48,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can see why the emperor gave you 
the title of "the Wise" at age six</font>

44
00:02:48,770 --> 00:02:52,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and appointed you 
minister-prince of justice.</font>

45
00:02:53,080 --> 00:02:55,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't need extra money,</font>

46
00:02:55,790 --> 00:02:57,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I will stop accepting bribes.</font>

47
00:02:57,720 --> 00:03:01,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please allow me to work for Your 
Highness from this day forward.</font>

48
00:03:02,420 --> 00:03:05,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I should be suspicious of 
ulterior motives, but...</i></font>

49
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:09,390
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#f9ffff"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Name</b></font></font></font>

50
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:09,390
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#f9ffff"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Noah Ararat  Minister-Prince of Justice</b></font></font></font>

51
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:09,390
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#f9ffff"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Sex</b></font></font></font>

52
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:09,390
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#f9ffff"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Male</b></font></font></font>

53
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:09,390
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#f9ffff"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Level</b></font></font></font>

54
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:09,390
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#f9ffff"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Fire</b></font></font></font>

55
00:03:08,890 --> 00:03:11,080
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="32"><font color="#fcffff"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Strength</b></font></font></font></font>

56
00:03:08,890 --> 00:03:11,080
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="32"><font color="#fcffff"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Stamina</b></font></font></font></font>

57
00:03:08,890 --> 00:03:11,080
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="32"><font color="#fcffff"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Intelligence</b></font></font></font></font>

58
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:13,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm counting on you, Viny.</font>

59
00:03:13,530 --> 00:03:14,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

60
00:03:33,580 --> 00:03:35,520
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#817c4f"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="10">Born Blessed, So I'll Obtain Ultimate Power</font></b></font></font></font>

61
00:03:33,580 --> 00:03:35,520
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#051529">m 0 0 l 235 0 l 225 8 l 235 15 l 18 15 l 30 8 l 18 0</font></font>

62
00:04:57,340 --> 00:05:04,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for arranging this grand 
celebration for me, Brother Oscar.</font>

63
00:05:04,230 --> 00:05:08,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'm happy, too. 
After our brother Henry,</font>

64
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:10,700
<font face="Times New Roman" size="18" color="#d7dad8"><b>{\an3}<font color="#ece6dd">Oscar Ararat
<font size="13">Eighth Prince</font></font></b></font>

65
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:12,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you're the second minister-prince in 
all of the emperor's fifty-year reign.</font>

66
00:05:13,050 --> 00:05:15,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Despite how it may seem, 
I quite like you.</font>

67
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:17,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me congratulate you.</font>

68
00:05:20,110 --> 00:05:21,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You aren't happy?</font>

69
00:05:21,900 --> 00:05:28,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It isn't that, but why did His Majesty 
appoint us as minister-princes?</font>

70
00:05:28,850 --> 00:05:30,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Probably because you're so dear to him.</font>

71
00:05:31,500 --> 00:05:33,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't completely rule that out.</i></font>

72
00:05:35,010 --> 00:05:39,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In Henry's case, he had the legitimate 
reason of suppressing the rebellion.</i></font>

73
00:05:40,630 --> 00:05:42,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't have that kind of record,</i></font>

74
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:46,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>so maybe it's natural to conclude that 
His Majesty is showing me favoritism.</i></font>

75
00:05:46,630 --> 00:05:47,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And yet...</i></font>

76
00:05:47,730 --> 00:05:53,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brother, you're aware the empire nearly
collapsed at one point, are you not?</font>

77
00:05:53,810 --> 00:05:54,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

78
00:05:58,180 --> 00:06:02,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It happened because of the empire's 
system of choosing a crown prince to rule.</i></font>

79
00:06:02,870 --> 00:06:06,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Because the emperor's successor 
is determined at birth,</i></font>

80
00:06:08,570 --> 00:06:12,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the princes who were not the crown 
prince idled their lives away,</i></font>

81
00:06:12,010 --> 00:06:15,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and domestic stability 
was drastically shaken.</i></font>

82
00:06:15,470 --> 00:06:17,430
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="13"><font face="Arial"><font color="#dcdcdc">Thirteenth Prince</font></font></font></font>

83
00:06:15,470 --> 00:06:19,350
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="13"><font face="Arial"><font color="#dcdcdc">Twelfth Prince</font></font></font></font>

84
00:06:15,470 --> 00:06:19,900
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="13"><font face="Arial"><font color="#dcdcdc">Eleventh Prince</font></font></font></font>

85
00:06:15,470 --> 00:06:22,150
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="13"><font face="Arial"><font color="#dcdcdc">Ninth Prince</font></font></font></font>

86
00:06:15,470 --> 00:06:22,940
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="13"><font face="Arial"><font color="#dcdcdc">Eighth Prince</font></font></font></font>

87
00:06:15,470 --> 00:06:20,020
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="13"><font face="Arial"><font color="#dcdcdc">Tenth Prince</font></font></font></font>

88
00:06:15,470 --> 00:06:23,070
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="13"><font face="Arial"><font color="#dcdcdc">Seventh Prince</font></font></font></font>

89
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:23,980
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="13"><font face="Arial"><font color="#dcdcdc">Imperial Castle</font></font></font></font>

90
00:06:15,770 --> 00:06:21,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Following introspection, the empire 
now grants every prince his own fief,</i></font>

91
00:06:18,100 --> 00:06:25,940
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="13"><font face="Arial"><font color="#dcdcdc">Sixth Prince</font></font></font></font>

92
00:06:18,980 --> 00:06:25,940
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="13"><font face="Arial"><font color="#dcdcdc">Fifth Prince</font></font></font></font>

93
00:06:19,350 --> 00:06:25,940
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="13"><font face="Arial"><font color="#dcdcdc">Fourth Prince</font></font></font></font>

94
00:06:21,610 --> 00:06:25,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and ensures they get a proper education.</i></font>

95
00:06:21,690 --> 00:06:25,940
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="13"><font face="Arial"><font color="#dcdcdc">Third Prince</font></font></font></font>

96
00:06:22,190 --> 00:06:25,940
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="13"><font face="Arial"><font color="#dcdcdc">First Prince</font></font></font></font>

97
00:06:22,230 --> 00:06:25,940
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="13"><font face="Arial"><font color="#dcdcdc">Second Prince</font></font></font></font>

98
00:06:25,940 --> 00:06:28,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what does that have to do with this?</font>

99
00:06:28,870 --> 00:06:33,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you think appointing me minister 
goes beyond "an education"?</font>

100
00:06:34,210 --> 00:06:35,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't mean...</font>

101
00:06:41,370 --> 00:06:44,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he wants to make <i>you</i> crown prince?</font>

102
00:06:44,790 --> 00:06:46,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know.</font>

103
00:06:46,310 --> 00:06:50,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If he's merely doting on me, 
there's no problem, but...</font>

104
00:06:51,970 --> 00:06:53,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness...</font>

105
00:06:56,060 --> 00:06:58,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Incredible. You were right.</font>

106
00:06:58,850 --> 00:06:59,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm?</font>

107
00:07:00,170 --> 00:07:03,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I received a report from 
a eunuch I've bought off.</font>

108
00:07:03,400 --> 00:07:05,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The emperor intends</font>

109
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:09,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to name me minister-prince of finance 
at tomorrow's morning assembly.</font>

110
00:07:11,380 --> 00:07:12,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It can't be...</font>

111
00:07:12,930 --> 00:07:15,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The emperor is making Albert...</i></font>

112
00:07:19,950 --> 00:07:21,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At any rate...</font>

113
00:07:21,530 --> 00:07:25,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">today, we're here to celebrate 
you and toast your intuition.</font>

114
00:07:25,770 --> 00:07:26,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

115
00:07:29,580 --> 00:07:30,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this?!</font>

116
00:07:33,690 --> 00:07:34,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop!</font>

117
00:07:44,080 --> 00:07:49,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am told that 167 were 
arrested, including Keats.</font>

118
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:53,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They intended to pressure
Your Majesty into abdicating and,</font>

119
00:07:53,230 --> 00:07:56,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">once you were deposed as emperor, have 
the crown prince assume the throne.</font>

120
00:07:57,080 --> 00:08:00,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They confessed to the very 
plot our intel indicated.</font>

121
00:08:03,090 --> 00:08:07,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He has been crown prince for
thirty years of my fifty-year reign.</font>

122
00:08:07,850 --> 00:08:10,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose he can wait no longer.</font>

123
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:15,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bear in mind that there is no evidence 
of the crown prince's involvement</font>

124
00:08:15,370 --> 00:08:17,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in this incident.</font>

125
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:21,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am aware. I won't do 
anything to Albert.</font>

126
00:08:21,760 --> 00:08:25,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This Keats man will be executed, 
and that will be the end of it.</font>

127
00:08:29,890 --> 00:08:32,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What became of the incident with Oscar?</font>

128
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:37,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have just sent out a eunuch who 
is friends with His Highness.</font>

129
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:40,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It would seem His Highness 
was aware of the situation.</font>

130
00:08:40,550 --> 00:08:41,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh?</font>

131
00:08:41,450 --> 00:08:44,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His Highness Noah was with him, as well.</font>

132
00:08:44,740 --> 00:08:48,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then it must have been Noah who 
caught on to my intentions.</font>

133
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:51,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">According to the report...</font>

134
00:08:52,030 --> 00:08:56,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course. Remarkable as ever, that Noah.</font>

135
00:08:58,720 --> 00:09:00,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gilbert is no good.</font>

136
00:09:01,020 --> 00:09:02,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Albert is no good.</font>

137
00:09:02,730 --> 00:09:07,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who, then? Who is worthy 
of succeeding me?</font>

138
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:10,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Henry? Oscar? Noah?</font>

139
00:09:14,510 --> 00:09:20,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Any of them will do as long 
as he can overcome my trial.</font>

140
00:09:21,830 --> 00:09:26,580
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#0b0700">Episode 7</font></b></font></font>

141
00:09:21,830 --> 00:09:26,580
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#0b0700">The Emperor's Wishes</font></b></font></font>

142
00:09:29,710 --> 00:09:34,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The aforementioned are the leader and 
accomplices in the attempted insurrection.</font>

143
00:09:36,180 --> 00:09:39,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And of course they're all 
people close to Albert.</font>

144
00:09:40,650 --> 00:09:45,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>His confidant, his former tutor,
his knights...</i></font>

145
00:09:45,740 --> 00:09:50,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Anyone would conclude that this was a 
revolt led by the crown prince's faction.</i></font>

146
00:09:51,490 --> 00:09:52,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What will you do?</font>

147
00:09:56,280 --> 00:09:58,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's the natural reaction.</i></font>

148
00:09:58,760 --> 00:10:01,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As for whether Albert had 
a hand in this or not...</i></font>

149
00:10:03,640 --> 00:10:07,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Under imperial law, if one of the 
imperial family commits a crime,</i></font>

150
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:11,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>there are provisions that ensure 
their penalty is light.</i></font>

151
00:10:11,760 --> 00:10:13,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But there is just one exception:</i></font>

152
00:10:15,170 --> 00:10:16,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>insurrection.</i></font>

153
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:19,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Any member of the imperial family 
who is involved in an insurrection</i></font>

154
00:10:20,870 --> 00:10:24,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>is to be cut in half at the waist, 
be they leader or accomplice.</i></font>

155
00:10:24,750 --> 00:10:28,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They face the same sentence if 
they are aware of the scheme</i></font>

156
00:10:28,690 --> 00:10:30,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and fail to report it to the emperor.</i></font>

157
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:33,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Given how many of his 
people are involved,</i></font>

158
00:10:33,770 --> 00:10:36,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>there's no way Albert 
didn't know about this.</i></font>

159
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:38,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But...</i></font>

160
00:10:38,770 --> 00:10:42,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The crown prince's 
insurrection and execution</i></font>

161
00:10:38,780 --> 00:10:42,950
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#e8e6e1"><b><font face="Times New Roman">Emperor</font></b></font></font>

162
00:10:38,780 --> 00:10:41,360
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="15"><font color="#e8e6e1"><b><font face="Times New Roman">Crown Prince, Second Prince</font></b></font></font></font>

163
00:10:38,780 --> 00:10:41,360
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="15"><font color="#e8e6e1"><b><font face="Times New Roman">Albert</font></b></font></font></font>

164
00:10:38,780 --> 00:10:42,950
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="15"><font color="#e8e6e1"><b><font face="Times New Roman">Third Prince</font></b></font></font></font>

165
00:10:38,780 --> 00:10:42,950
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="15"><font color="#e8e6e1"><b><font face="Times New Roman">Kiro</font></b></font></font></font>

166
00:10:43,450 --> 00:10:49,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>would be a massive scandal that shakes 
the very foundation of the empire.</i></font>

167
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:52,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What has the emperor said?</font>

168
00:10:52,610 --> 00:10:56,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He said to state the relevant law,</font>

169
00:10:56,110 --> 00:10:59,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and to punish those involved accordingly.</font>

170
00:10:59,680 --> 00:11:01,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

171
00:11:01,670 --> 00:11:03,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I now understand the 
emperor's intentions.</font>

172
00:11:06,480 --> 00:11:08,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will now pass judgment.</font>

173
00:11:17,550 --> 00:11:18,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

174
00:11:19,910 --> 00:11:23,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have decided how to 
sentence the insurgents.</font>

175
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:25,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Proceed.</font>

176
00:11:25,790 --> 00:11:30,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From among those who were arrested, the 
leader will be cut in half at the waist,</font>

177
00:11:30,660 --> 00:11:32,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the accomplices will be executed.</font>

178
00:11:33,070 --> 00:11:36,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The executions will be carried out
as soon as they are sentenced.</font>

179
00:11:39,250 --> 00:11:41,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The fact that he limited 
it only to those arrested</i></font>

180
00:11:41,820 --> 00:11:45,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>must mean that he currently has no 
intention of bringing Albert into this.</i></font>

181
00:11:46,410 --> 00:11:50,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That means only those on 
the list will be judged.</i></font>

182
00:11:51,280 --> 00:11:53,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I could postpone their deaths</i></font>

183
00:11:53,040 --> 00:11:56,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>until the day of the year when 
all executions are carried out.</i></font>

184
00:11:57,020 --> 00:12:02,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But Albert's involvement could be revealed,
through a pardon or something similar.</i></font>

185
00:12:02,910 --> 00:12:05,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So I must execute them as soon as possible.</i></font>

186
00:12:06,170 --> 00:12:08,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is all within the 
bounds of imperial law.</i></font>

187
00:12:09,610 --> 00:12:11,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well done.</font>

188
00:12:12,510 --> 00:12:13,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cruz.</font>

189
00:12:13,660 --> 00:12:14,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Majesty.</font>

190
00:12:14,620 --> 00:12:16,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Noah has done well.</font>

191
00:12:17,140 --> 00:12:20,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Add a thousand rean to his annual salary.</font>

192
00:12:20,430 --> 00:12:24,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is not a feat worthy of a reward.</i></font>

193
00:12:24,770 --> 00:12:28,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He really didn't want to 
get Albert involved in this.</i></font>

194
00:12:28,980 --> 00:12:30,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brilliant as usual, Noah.</font>

195
00:12:31,490 --> 00:12:35,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My hopes for you remain high. 
Keep up the good work.</font>

196
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:46,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness!</font>

197
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:55,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! What happened?</font>

198
00:12:56,610 --> 00:12:57,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your... Highness...</font>

199
00:12:57,830 --> 00:13:02,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Intruders... still... inside...</font>

200
00:13:02,830 --> 00:13:03,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

201
00:13:05,830 --> 00:13:07,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Send for reinforcements!</font>

202
00:13:07,610 --> 00:13:09,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ask my brother at the Ministry 
of Military Affairs toâ€”</font>

203
00:13:09,770 --> 00:13:11,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait... The timing of this...</i></font>

204
00:13:12,670 --> 00:13:13,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

205
00:13:14,160 --> 00:13:16,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gather our allies!</font>

206
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:19,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let no one inside or outside 
the mansion other than me,</font>

207
00:13:19,790 --> 00:13:21,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">even the other princes!</font>

208
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:23,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood.</font>

209
00:13:31,650 --> 00:13:33,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Your Highness...</font>

210
00:13:34,240 --> 00:13:35,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All officials, stand down!</font>

211
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:43,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not good enough!</font>

212
00:13:46,630 --> 00:13:47,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it!</font>

213
00:13:48,270 --> 00:13:49,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't let you commit suicide.</font>

214
00:13:50,340 --> 00:13:52,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! We're pulling out!</font>

215
00:14:04,780 --> 00:14:05,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impossible!</font>

216
00:14:13,940 --> 00:14:15,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness!</font>

217
00:14:17,820 --> 00:14:21,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't believe it... 
You defeated them all?</font>

218
00:14:21,280 --> 00:14:22,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Incredible...</font>

219
00:14:22,810 --> 00:14:23,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the situation?</font>

220
00:14:24,320 --> 00:14:27,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can see the casualties 
among our guards.</font>

221
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:31,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And all the insurgents were killed.</font>

222
00:14:32,820 --> 00:14:34,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All of them?</font>

223
00:14:35,760 --> 00:14:37,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They were silenced.</i></font>

224
00:14:38,800 --> 00:14:42,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In other words, these are Albert's...</i></font>

225
00:14:42,770 --> 00:14:44,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the crown prince's men.</i></font>

226
00:14:50,680 --> 00:14:51,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness?!</font>

227
00:14:52,680 --> 00:14:54,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness! What are you...</font>

228
00:14:57,210 --> 00:14:59,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These four did this to me.</font>

229
00:14:59,380 --> 00:15:04,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is the heaviest punishment 
for severely wounding a prince?</font>

230
00:15:06,900 --> 00:15:10,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Execution in all cases, 
and by summary judgment.</font>

231
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:12,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then do that immediately!</font>

232
00:15:12,640 --> 00:15:13,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course!</font>

233
00:15:28,880 --> 00:15:31,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The executions have been carried out.</font>

234
00:15:31,370 --> 00:15:35,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good. Now this whole matter is over.</font>

235
00:15:35,930 --> 00:15:38,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness never ceases to amaze.</font>

236
00:15:43,010 --> 00:15:47,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I swear... One misstep and the whole 
empire would've been on the rocks.</i></font>

237
00:15:47,260 --> 00:15:48,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Damned crown prince.</i></font>

238
00:15:53,160 --> 00:15:54,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pardon me.</font>

239
00:15:56,260 --> 00:15:58,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry to summon you here.</font>

240
00:15:58,750 --> 00:16:02,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are wounded, no less. 
There's no need for formality.</font>

241
00:16:03,400 --> 00:16:04,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Your Majesty.</font>

242
00:16:05,430 --> 00:16:09,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could not be more 
ashamed at my failure.</font>

243
00:16:10,110 --> 00:16:13,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter. You are not solely to blame.</font>

244
00:16:14,940 --> 00:16:19,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, to think they wounded 
a man of your caliber.</font>

245
00:16:19,950 --> 00:16:22,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were they truly so capable?</font>

246
00:16:23,280 --> 00:16:25,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I figured he would ask that.</i></font>

247
00:16:25,580 --> 00:16:27,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Given his intelligence network,</i></font>

248
00:16:28,100 --> 00:16:32,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>he probably already knows that 
I gave myself this wound.</i></font>

249
00:16:33,040 --> 00:16:34,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I believe that strength...</font>

250
00:16:36,250 --> 00:16:39,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is not solely dependent on 
one's skill with the sword.</font>

251
00:16:39,450 --> 00:16:41,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter how talented one is,</font>

252
00:16:41,690 --> 00:16:45,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he can falter if his mental 
fragility is taken advantage of.</font>

253
00:16:45,890 --> 00:16:49,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. Truly, I have a fine son...</font>

254
00:16:49,110 --> 00:16:53,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">no, a son I would be proud 
to present to all.</font>

255
00:16:53,930 --> 00:16:59,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It appears he understands the amount 
of thought I put into handling that.</i></font>

256
00:16:59,800 --> 00:17:03,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I only wish all my sons were like you.</font>

257
00:17:07,790 --> 00:17:09,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you walk with me?</font>

258
00:17:15,580 --> 00:17:17,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you know, Noah,</font>

259
00:17:18,450 --> 00:17:21,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">among emperors who come 
to be known as great leaders,</font>

260
00:17:21,530 --> 00:17:25,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">nine out of ten tarnish their 
reputation later in life.</font>

261
00:17:26,710 --> 00:17:29,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is he talking about the
crown prince's insurrection?</i></font>

262
00:17:31,730 --> 00:17:35,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Our emperor led this nation into a golden 
age like none it had known before.</i></font>

263
00:17:35,840 --> 00:17:39,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He will most certainly be described 
as a great leader in history books.</i></font>

264
00:17:40,420 --> 00:17:43,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But if that insurrection 
had been successful,</i></font>

265
00:17:43,960 --> 00:17:47,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>they would say he grew 
senile in his old age</i></font>

266
00:17:48,470 --> 00:17:50,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and couldn't even control his own sons.</i></font>

267
00:17:51,610 --> 00:17:55,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Clearly, the emperor no longer 
trusts the crown prince.</i></font>

268
00:17:56,330 --> 00:17:58,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The reason he won't do 
anything about it now</i></font>

269
00:17:59,160 --> 00:18:01,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>is because the very act of 
forsaking the crown prince</i></font>

270
00:18:02,210 --> 00:18:04,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>would tarnish his reputation 
in his later years.</i></font>

271
00:18:05,910 --> 00:18:10,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Majesty, if I may, 
I have a favor to ask.</font>

272
00:18:10,650 --> 00:18:11,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

273
00:18:11,900 --> 00:18:18,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You appointed Henry, Oscar, 
and myself minister-princes,</font>

274
00:18:19,360 --> 00:18:21,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but as that in itself is a first,</font>

275
00:18:22,140 --> 00:18:24,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I fear some aspects of it will be handled 
poorly somewhere down the line.</font>

276
00:18:25,360 --> 00:18:31,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I would appreciate it if you could 
appoint someone to coordinate all of us.</font>

277
00:18:31,530 --> 00:18:34,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you asking for my 
first prime minister?</font>

278
00:18:34,450 --> 00:18:38,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, as an example, you could appoint 
someone above the three of us</font>

279
00:18:38,830 --> 00:18:40,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to bring order to all that we do.</font>

280
00:18:41,070 --> 00:18:46,850
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="40"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#fffffe">Prime Minister-Prince</font></b></font></font></font>

281
00:18:41,350 --> 00:18:45,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am proposing the establishment of a new 
role known as the prime minister-prince.</font>

282
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:53,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I would like His Highness the 
Crown Prince to fill that role.</font>

283
00:18:55,050 --> 00:18:56,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impossible.</font>

284
00:18:58,520 --> 00:19:02,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your wounds aren't healed yet.
Leave for today.</font>

285
00:19:05,670 --> 00:19:08,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A crown prince of thirty years...</font>

286
00:19:09,540 --> 00:19:13,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can understand why my brother 
would begin to feel impatient.</font>

287
00:19:13,900 --> 00:19:15,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In which case...</font>

288
00:19:15,290 --> 00:19:18,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Your Majesty would still have 
the final say in all decisions.</font>

289
00:19:15,690 --> 00:19:22,970
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="40"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#fcffff">Emperor</font></b></font></font></font>

290
00:19:18,820 --> 00:19:22,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}You need only allow him to emulate you.</font>

291
00:19:19,050 --> 00:19:22,970
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="32"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#fcffff">Prime Minister-Prince</font></b></font></font></font>

292
00:19:22,970 --> 00:19:26,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But he would still rank above 
the ministers, would he not?</font>

293
00:19:26,930 --> 00:19:30,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What if the prime minister 
dismisses an important matter</font>

294
00:19:26,930 --> 00:19:32,890
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="10"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#fdfeff"><b>Minister-Prince
of Finance</b></font></font></font></font>

295
00:19:26,930 --> 00:19:32,890
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="10"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#fdfeff"><b>Minister-Prince
of Justice</b></font></font></font></font>

296
00:19:26,930 --> 00:19:32,890
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="10"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#fdfeff"><b>Minister-Prince
of Military Affairs</b></font></font></font></font>

297
00:19:26,950 --> 00:19:32,890
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="32"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#fdfeff"><b>Prime Minister-Prince</b></font></font></font></font>

298
00:19:30,150 --> 00:19:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and it never reaches me at all?</font>

299
00:19:30,250 --> 00:19:32,890
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="15"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#fdfeff"><b>(Final Say)</b></font></font></font></font>

300
00:19:30,250 --> 00:19:32,890
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="32"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#fdfeff"><b>Emperor</b></font></font></font></font>

301
00:19:32,890 --> 00:19:34,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To prevent that,</font>

302
00:19:34,990 --> 00:19:39,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">each minister-prince will have the 
right to file a direct appeal.</font>

303
00:19:39,190 --> 00:19:46,660
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="10"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#fdfeff"><b>Minister-Prince
of Finance</b></font></font></font></font>

304
00:19:39,190 --> 00:19:46,660
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="10"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#fdfeff"><b>Minister-Prince
of Justice</b></font></font></font></font>

305
00:19:39,190 --> 00:19:46,660
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="10"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#fdfeff"><b>Minister-Prince
of Military Affairs</b></font></font></font></font>

306
00:19:39,210 --> 00:19:46,660
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="32"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#fdfeff"><b>Prime Minister-Prince</b></font></font></font></font>

307
00:19:39,560 --> 00:19:42,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If all of us feel equally 
strongly about the matter,</font>

308
00:19:42,430 --> 00:19:45,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we can bypass the prime minister 
and appeal directly to you.</font>

309
00:19:43,320 --> 00:19:46,660
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="15"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#fdfeff"><b>(Can Directly
Appeal)</b></font></font></font></font>

310
00:19:43,320 --> 00:19:46,660
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="15"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#fdfeff"><b>(Final Say)</b></font></font></font></font>

311
00:19:43,340 --> 00:19:46,660
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="32"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#fdfeff"><b>Emperor</b></font></font></font></font>

312
00:19:49,130 --> 00:19:53,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That prevents the crown prince 
from holding any actual power.</i></font>

313
00:19:53,030 --> 00:19:58,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It doesn't matter if the prime 
minister-prince's role has any substance.</i></font>

314
00:19:58,190 --> 00:20:00,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It will be no more than a title.</i></font>

315
00:20:04,240 --> 00:20:05,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Remarkable.</font>

316
00:20:09,080 --> 00:20:13,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are right. If that will 
work, it is the best choice.</font>

317
00:20:13,470 --> 00:20:16,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for your counsel, Noah.</font>

318
00:20:16,790 --> 00:20:19,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Consider it delivered to the throne.</font>

319
00:20:19,560 --> 00:20:21,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am most grateful.</font>

320
00:20:25,590 --> 00:20:30,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It truly is a shame you 
weren't born sooner.</font>

321
00:20:30,830 --> 00:20:34,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He understood my proposal instantly.</i></font>

322
00:20:34,690 --> 00:20:37,330
